 <div class="hero-content"><div class="hero-tag">Compliance Reference &middot; Security</div><div class="hero-title">ISO/IEC 27001:2022<br><span class="accent">Information Security</span></div><div class="hero-subtitle">A Practical Compliance Reference for our team</div><div class="hero-desc">What the standard is and what certification means versus SOC 2, the full road to a compliant ISMS, the mandatory documentation a compliance officer must keep, how the audit works, the controls and processes it incorporates, and how our organization keeps the certificate alive.</div><button type="button" class="hero-scroll" data-show-section="iso27001-c1">Start Reading <span class="hero-scroll-arrow">&darr;</span></button></div>
